graph TB
    START([Start]):::state
    -->|1. Build Context| Context[Context Injection<br/>profile + behavior + memories]:::process
    
    Context -->|2. LLM Reason| LLM[LLM Reasoning<br/>gemini-3.1-flash-lite<br/>retry 3x, timeout 90s]:::llm
    
    LLM --> HasTools{Has tool_calls?}:::decision
    
    HasTools -->|No| Answer[Return Final Answer<br/>with personalization]:::done
    HasTools -->|Yes| Dupe{Duplicate?}:::decision2
    
    Dupe -->|Yes| LLM
    Dupe -->|No| Exec[Execute Tool<br/>validate inputs<br/>check sensitive<br/>timeout 30s]:::process
    
    Exec --> LLM
    
    LLM --> LoopCheck{Iteration >= 4?}:::decision
    LoopCheck -->|No| LLM
    LoopCheck -->|Yes| Breaker[Loop Breaker<br/>fallback: contact phone]:::done
    
    Answer --> END([End]):::state
    Breaker --> END
    
